author: Dan Snierson
title: NFL Mean Tweets: Russell Wilson, Tony Romo, J.J. Watt read insults
text:
Email 
This Sunday brings a torrent of tackles as Super Bowl LI kicks off, but the brutal hits have already started. Tonight on Jimmy Kimmel Live , NFL stars will tackle the tough topic of themselves, reciting nasty comments culled from the Twittersphere. 
Click on the preview above to see J.J. Watt read this gem, “J.J. Watt kinda looks like a fat Macklemore.” Russell Wilson and Tony Romo also get roughed up. 
Jimmy Kimmel Live airs weeknights at 11:35 p.m. ET/PT on ABC. Show Full Article
